# Keep the build context small and reproducible.
#
# The image build resolves `edgecommons` from the pinned git rev (needs network + git auth), NOT
# the local sibling override — so the gitignored `.cargo/config.toml` patch must never enter the
# context, or the build would try to read a host path that does not exist in the image.
.cargo/
target/
greengrass-build/
logs/
*.metric.log
.git/
